{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 VibeSwap Autonomous Partnership Framework\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b W. Glynn, JARVIS} {\b March 2026 | VibeSwap}\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Executive Summary\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 VibeSwap uses an autonomous partnership pipeline \u8212- codename {\b Karma} \u8212- that continuously discovers, evaluates, contacts, and tracks potential protocol partners. The system runs with minimal human intervention, surfacing only high-quality opportunities for final approval.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Karma replaces the traditional BD model (one person cold-emailing) with a structured, repeatable, autonomous workflow that any team member can operate and any AI agent can execute.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
