{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 2.2 Discovery Criteria\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A project enters the pipeline if it matches ANY of:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Building MEV protection or fair ordering\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Building batch auction infrastructure\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Building AI agent infrastructure\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Building cross-chain DEX or bridge infrastructure\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Active on a chain VibeSwap deploys on (Base, Arbitrum, Optimism, CKB)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Has expressed interest in Cooperative Capitalism or similar economic models\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 2.3 Implementation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Phase 1 (manual + templates): - Weekly 30-minute discovery session using Twitter search, DeFi Llama, and GitHub - Log prospects in a shared spreadsheet or Notion database\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Phase 2 (semi-automated): - Scrapling-based web scraper monitors sources automatically - Generates discovery report delivered to Telegram/Discord - Human reviews and approves entries into pipeline\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Phase 3 (fully autonomous): - JARVIS runs discovery autonomously using web search + API tools - Auto-populates CRM with scored prospects - Human only reviews final outreach drafts\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
