{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 5.3 Integration Types\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Technical Integration}: Shared smart contracts, cross-protocol calls\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Liquidity Partnership}: Shared pools, cross-listed assets\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Research Collaboration}: Co-authored papers, shared mechanism design\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Co-Marketing}: Joint announcements, shared content, cross-promotion\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Ecosystem Grant}: Funding from partner ecosystem for VibeSwap deployment\sa180\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 6. Stage 5: Execution\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 6.1 On-Chain Partnership Contracts\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For technical and liquidity partnerships, terms are encoded in smart contracts:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 struct Partnership \{\line
    address partner;\line
    uint256 revenueShareBps;    // Partner's share in basis points\line
    uint256 startBlock;\line
    uint256 endBlock;           // 0 = indefinite\line
    bytes32 integrationHash;    // Hash of integration spec\line
    bool active;\line
\}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 6.2 Milestone Structure\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Each partnership has 3 milestones:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab {\b Integration Complete}: Smart contracts deployed, interoperability verified\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab {\b Volume Threshold}: $X monthly volume flowing through partnership\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab {\b Community Adoption}: Y unique users from partner community\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Revenue sharing activates at Milestone 1. Bonus allocation at Milestones 2 and 3.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 6.3 Revenue Sharing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Default: 50/50 split on cross-protocol fees generated by the partnership.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Partner-originated swaps (referred by partner UI or contracts) generate fees that are split: - 50% to VibeSwap Shapley pool - 50% to partner treasury\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This aligns incentives: both sides benefit from driving volume through the integration.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
