{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 8. Karma for JARVIS\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 JARVIS can execute the Karma loop autonomously:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab {\b Discovery}: Use web search tools to find prospects matching criteria\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab {\b Evaluation}: Score using the matrix, classify into tiers\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab {\b Outreach}: Draft personalized emails for human approval\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab {\b Tracking}: Update CRM entries after each interaction\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 5.\tx360\tab {\b Reporting}: Generate weekly reports and surface action items\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Human involvement: Review outreach drafts, attend meetings, approve deal terms. Everything else is autonomous.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\i Partnerships should be autonomous. We don\u8217't chase \u8212- we attract through technical credibility and execute through structured process.}\par}
